@startuml async-messaging
title ClearEyeQ — Azure Service Bus Event Map

skinparam rectangleRoundCorner 8
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

rectangle "**Scan Engine**" as scan #E3F2FD
rectangle "**Monitoring**" as monitor #E3F2FD
rectangle "**Environmental**" as env #E3F2FD
rectangle "**Diagnostic Engine**" as diag #FFF3E0
rectangle "**Predictive Engine**" as predict #FFF3E0
rectangle "**Treatment**" as treat #E8F5E9
rectangle "**Clinical Portal**" as portal #F5F5F5
rectangle "**Billing**" as billing #F3E5F5

rectangle "**Transactional Outbox Relay**\n(applies per publisher service)" as outbox #FFFDE7
rectangle "**Inbox / Processed Message Store**\n(applies per subscriber service)" as inbox #E8F5E9

queue "ScanCompleted" as q1
queue "MonitoringDataReceived" as q2
queue "EnvironmentalSnapshotCaptured" as q3
queue "DiagnosisCompleted" as q4
queue "ForecastGenerated" as q5
queue "FlareUpWarning" as q6
queue "TreatmentPlanProposed" as q7
queue "TreatmentPlanApproved" as q8
queue "TreatmentPlanActivated" as q9
queue "TreatmentAdjustmentProposed" as q10
queue "TreatmentAdjustmentApproved" as q11
queue "InterventionAdjusted" as q12
queue "EscalationRecommended" as q13
queue "SubscriptionChanged" as q14

rectangle "**Diagnostic Engine**\n(Subscriber)" as diagSub #FFF3E0
rectangle "**Predictive Engine**\n(Subscriber)" as predictSub #FFF3E0
rectangle "**Treatment**\n(Subscriber)" as treatSub #E8F5E9
rectangle "**Notifications**\n(Subscriber)" as notifSub #FCE4EC
rectangle "**Clinical Portal**\n(Subscriber)" as clinicSub #F5F5F5
rectangle "**FHIR**\n(Subscriber)" as fhirSub #F5F5F5
rectangle "**All Services**\n(Subscriber)" as allSub #F5F5F5

scan --> outbox
monitor --> outbox
env --> outbox
diag --> outbox
predict --> outbox
treat --> outbox
portal --> outbox
billing --> outbox

outbox --> q1
outbox --> q2
outbox --> q3
outbox --> q4
outbox --> q5
outbox --> q6
outbox --> q7
outbox --> q8
outbox --> q9
outbox --> q10
outbox --> q11
outbox --> q12
outbox --> q13
outbox --> q14

q1 --> inbox
q2 --> inbox
q3 --> inbox
q4 --> inbox
q5 --> inbox
q6 --> inbox
q7 --> inbox
q8 --> inbox
q9 --> inbox
q10 --> inbox
q11 --> inbox
q12 --> inbox
q13 --> inbox
q14 --> inbox

inbox --> diagSub
inbox --> predictSub
inbox --> treatSub
inbox --> notifSub
inbox --> clinicSub
inbox --> fhirSub
inbox --> allSub

note right of q4
Event envelope fields:
- EventId
- SchemaVersion
- TenantId
- SubjectId
- CorrelationId
- CausationId
- OccurredAtUtc
end note

note bottom of inbox
Consumers are idempotent.
Failures use retry with backoff, then DLQ.
Replay tooling rehydrates projections from the outbox archive.
end note

@enduml
